snippet.title: Mine Shaft: Ludum Dare 48 Project - Trailer
snippet.description:
This is a short "trailer"-like video presenting the game me and my friend have made over the course of last weekend (less than 72 hours) in Unity for our first game-jam event.

You can play it here:
https://krzyhau.itch.io/mine-shaft

Ludum Dare 48 page:
https://ldjam.com/events/ludum-dare/48/mine-shaft
